These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, animation
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, roller
1. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | animation |
| Transport     | roller | skateboard  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: apricot, lemon
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, water-polo
1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | apricot      | lemon         |
| Sport   | handball | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea
There 2 different types of food: grapefruit, pineapple
1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | water   |
| Food       | pineapple  | grapefruit |

 #################################

 
